Create the dynamic background shape for 12 Area Charts 20

 Create 1st background shape for bus passengers

-        Bring the shape rectangle shape to the report pane

-        Format

    General > X position = 0, Y position= 426, Width = 306, Height= 97 > Place the rectangle shape above the Bus passenger Area chart

 

   Line > Weight = 2

   Fill > Off



Create all other 11 background shape for other Area chart  

-        Copy background shape created to the bus passenger (Control + C) and paste (Control + V) to other area chart

-        Repeat this for all other area chart measures.
